This page on SteamDB lists all Steam games tagged as '2D Fighter'. The '2D Fighter' tag is used for games that feature two-dimensional (2D) combat mechanics, similar to classic arcade fighters. Players engage in one-on-one or team battles with a variety of characters, each with unique abilities and move sets. The games may include various modes such as arcade, versus, and tournament. This tag covers a wide range of genres from action to fighting to platformers, making for an eclectic collection of games. The page is updated automatically to reflect any new or removed games tagged as '2D Fighter'.
